data.name: TxtStatus.ToolTip
data.value: Shows current status of run. Awairing Start- Ready to start a new cure, preheat or log Preheat in Progress- Part is currently preheating Cure in Progress- Cure is being executed Cure Complete- Cure is complete and the part is ready for further processing.

data.name: DGVPID.ToolTip
data.value: This shows the current PID settings at the controller. These settings are specific to each part and are updated when a new part is entered. Change the PID settings at the temperature controller by inputing new values and pressing Send PID Settings button.
